    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
