    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather remains supple and taut, free from any creases or bolster wear, and still retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions flawlessly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized centers with a complete, documented paper trail. This is a rare, collector-grade example for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
